{"tid":95762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【損失慘重】再有電話騙案　六旬婦失1200萬元","createTime":"2017-01-26T09:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T13:31:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdd18082a3bc2ee7f1c3769fdf628374103f17d","tid":95762,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170126/s00001/1485421341578SL4_F07F4D14BC99D333A0F7631696F46AA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170126%2Fs00001%2F1485421341578SL4_F07F4D14BC99D333A0F7631696F46AA8.jpg&h=9bc3c7d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨近新春再有受害人誤墮電話騙案。一名64歲婦人去年11月在香港接獲一名男子來電，對方自稱為速遞公司職員，聲稱她有包裹正受內地執法機關人員調查，其間將通話轉駁至一名女子，該女子聲稱為內地執法機關人員，指包裹涉及刑事案件。<br />\n<br />\n其後，婦人分別在香港及澳門多次收到另一名男子來電，多次要求她匯款至兩個內地戶口，作調查之用，婦人不虞有詐，先後在港澳總共匯款約1200萬元，其後懷疑被騙，遂到北角警署向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n案件交由東九龍總區重案組第3隊跟進，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170126/s00001/1485421410281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170126%2Fs00001%2F1485421410281&d=cxYmfqVuV6muW8ojATK39nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=af500616\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170126%2Fs00001%2F1485421410281&h=3d064326\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170126/s00001/1485421410281</a>"},{"pid":"0e580a8c2d42dda6e23915bec1a33eb0e0897b1d","tid":95762,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f15c1cb2b66457afc499126792a26c3c63532d68","tid":95762,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"咁就千幾萬，發發了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6b44e2eb02831a24d9dd189abf923ee97100cc","tid":95